; ******************************************************************************
; *                                                                            *
; *                   TEST NEW CLOTHING SYSTEM: WEAR/REMOVE                    *
; *                                                                            *
; ******************************************************************************
; This script is designed to test the 'WEAR'and 'REMOVE' verbs of the new
; clothing system, which doesn't use the 'worn' entity any more to store clothes
; worn by Hero.
; ** NOTE ** ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
;            The new 'WEAR'and 'REMOVE' verbs only use `donned` to do their
;            magic! No need to check 'wearing'set!
;            (they do still set it, but don't use it in calculations)
;            ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
north
north
inventory
; ==============================================================================
; CAN'T WEAR ITEMS
; ==============================================================================
wear skirt
wear dungarees
wear pantyhose
wear jeans
; ==============================================================================
; CAN'T REMOVE ITEMS
; ==============================================================================
remove socks
DBG socks
remove boxers
DBG boxers
; ==============================================================================
; REMOVE ITEMS
; ==============================================================================
remove sneakers
DBG sneakers
remove socks
DBG socks
remove khakis
DBG khakis
remove boxers
DBG boxers
remove undershirt
DBG undershirt
; ==============================================================================
; WEAR ITEMS
; ==============================================================================
wear dungarees
DBG dungarees
remove dungarees
wear jeans
DBG jeans
remove jeans
; ==============================================================================
; WEAR ITEMS -> Skirt THEN Pantyhose
; ==============================================================================
; Check that the old system of skirt exception still works:
wear skirt
DBG skirt
wear pantyhose
DBG pantyhose
